# Email Sanitizer (Strict v1)

## Description

Sanitizes an email string by:

- trimming whitespace
- forcing lowercase
- removing whitespace
- removing non-email-safe characters

Stateless and deterministic.

---

## Endpoint

POST /v1/sanitize-email

---

## Payload

{
  "input": "  Rick+Test@Example.COM  "
}

---

## Response

{
  "output": "rick+test@example.com"
}

---

## Health

GET /health

---

## Non-Expansion Clause

This API sanitizes characters only.

It will never:

- validate deliverability
- check MX records
- fix malformed emails
- expand scope
